The issue in your code is that there is a syntax error when you are creating the form. To correctly initialize the `inputBaseUnit` formControl as a `required` field, use the below syntax.
```js
this.itemForm = this.fb.group({ 
    inputBaseUnit: [&#39;&#39;, [Validators.required]],
});
```
where `&#39;&#39;` is the initial value of your `ng-select`

Since you have only one `Validator`, you can shorten the above code like so
```js
this.itemForm = this.fb.group({ 
    inputBaseUnit: [&#39;&#39;, Validators.required],
});
```

